Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IItem

    public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
implements IItem
    A physical instance of a particular Product. An Item corresponds to a physical container with a barcode on it.
    Author:
    Daniel Carrier

        container - The product group this item is to be placed in, or the storage unit if it has no product group
